<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٥٢ -<span class="c5"> حدَّثنا آدَمُ:</span> حدَّثنا شُعْبَةُ: حدَّثنا ثابِتٌ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٦٣٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عن أَنَسِ بنِ مالِكٍ <span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> قالَ:</span> مَرَّ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِامْرَأَةٍ عِنْدَ قَبْرٍ وَهِيَ تَبْكِي،<span class="c5"> فقالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«اتَّقِي اللَّهَ واصْبِرِي»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>